# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI-generated output artifacts
#
# These files are OUTPUTS of the skill when used in a
# project. They belong in that project's repository, not in
# this skill repository. Excluding them here prevents
# accidental commits of project-specific state.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
HANDOVER.md
HANDOVER-*.md
.ai-context/
ai-risk-register.md
AI-WORKFLOW.md
ai-eval-rubric.md
tooling-compatibility.md

# CLAUDE.md and AGENTS.md are also output artifacts, but
# they are intentionally tracked in project repos.
# Excluded here because they don't belong in the skill repo
# itself — only in repositories that ADOPT the skill.
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
.cursorrules
